lead_paragraph: WITH THE UNITED STATES MARINES ON TARAWA, Nov. 27 (Delayed) (AP) -- Admiral Chester W. Nimitz, commander of the Pacific area, visited today the battle-scarred Tarawa atoll of the Gilbert Islands, invaded a week ago.
